data.title: Shaquille O'Neal (Basketball Player)
data.meta_description: Won three consecutive NBA championships from 2000-2002 as a member of the Los Angeles Lakers. Won a fourth NBA championship as a member of the Miami Heat in...
data.text:
Profession: Basketball Player

Biography: Won three consecutive NBA championships from 2000-2002 as a member of the Los Angeles Lakers. Won a fourth NBA championship as a member of the Miami Heat in 2006.

Also won the 1999-2000 MVP award and three NBA Finals MVP awards. Ranks 3rd all-time in field goal percentage (58.2%), largely because of his ability to dunk the basketball.

Born: March 6, 1972

Birthplace: Newark, New Jersey, USA

Age: 52 years old
